---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section id="experience" class="max-md:w-full w-5/6 mx-auto mt-48">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <h1
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-anchor-placement="center-bottom"
      class="mb-8 font-extrabold text-center text-4xl text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#d7d7d7] to-[#616161] sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl"
    >
      Experience
    </h1>
    <p
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-anchor-placement="center-bottom"
      class="text-gray-400 text-center text-lg font-semibold"
    >
      This section tells about my professional journey in tech field
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center mt-16 max-md:w-5/6 w-3/4">
      <span class="w-1 bg-primary bg-opacity-25 rounded-md"></span>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 w-full">
        <!-- Sameeksha Capital Internship -->
        <div class="text-primary font-semibold">
          <div class="flex gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <span
              data-aos="fade-right"
              class="-ml-[16px] absolute animate-ping inline-flex w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-orange-500 opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <div
              data-aos="fade-up"
              class="timeline-card border-l-4 border-l-orange-500 flex flex-row border-primary/10 border-[1px] bg-primary/10 py-4 bg-opacity-10 max-md:px-2 px-8 w-full"
            >
              <div
                class="max-md:hidden visible flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 min-w-[3rem] text-3xl font-bold text-green-500"
              >
                <img
                  src="/VrajDobariya.github.io/sameekshacapital.png"
                  alt="Sameeksha Capital"
                  class="h-15 w-15 object-contain"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col ml-6 w-full">
                <div
                  class="flex max-md:flex-col flex-row max-md:text-base text-2xl justify-between"
                >
                  <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <h1>Software Dev Engineer Intern</h1>
                    <p>
                      At <span class="text-indigo-300">Sameeksha Capital</span>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-right max-md:text-left">
                    From Jan 2026 to Current
                  </p>
                </div>
                <span
                  class="h-0.5 mt-4 w-full bg-primary bg-opacity-25 rounded-md"
                ></span>
                <ul
                  class="mt-4 max-md:text-sm text-xl font-light list-disc ml-5"
                >
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Optimized backend infrastructure by upgrading to <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">Django 5.x</span
                    > and offloading daily-to-monthly OHLCV market data aggregations
                    to <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >PostgreSQL</span
                    >, reducing analytics latency by <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">90%</span
                    > (60s → 6s).
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Engineered <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Python/GCP scraping pipelines</span
                    > and an AI ingestion framework (Gemini, Claude) with chunking,
                    retry logic, and approval queues to normalize <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >900+ unstructured reports</span
                    > into the database.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Architected a comprehensive <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">RBAC system</span
                    > across the React/DRF stack, and streamlined CI/CD by integrating
                    <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Bitbucket pipelines</span
                    > for automated LLM-based PR reviews.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Google Internship -->
        <div class="text-primary font-semibold">
          <div class="flex gap-8 h-full items-center">
            <span
              data-aos="fade-right"
              class="-ml-[16px] absolute inline-flex w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-sky-400 opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <div
              data-aos="fade-up"
              class="timeline-card border-l-4 border-l-sky-400 flex flex-row border-primary/10 border-[1px] bg-primary/10 py-4 bg-opacity-10 max-md:px-2 px-8 w-full"
            >
              <div
                class="max-md:hidden visible flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 min-w-[3rem] text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500"
              >
                <img
                  src="/VrajDobariya.github.io/GoogleLogo.png"
                  alt="Google"
                  class="flex h-10 w-10 mt-2 object-contain"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col ml-6 w-full">
                <div
                  class="flex max-md:flex-col flex-row max-md:text-base text-2xl justify-between"
                >
                  <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <h1>Software Engineer Intern</h1>
                    <p>
                      At <span class="text-indigo-300">Google</span> • Bengaluru
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-right max-md:text-left">
                    From May 2025 to July 2025
                  </p>
                </div>

                <span
                  class="h-0.5 mt-4 w-full bg-primary bg-opacity-25 rounded-md"
                ></span>

                <ul
                  class="mt-4 max-md:text-sm text-xl font-light list-disc ml-5"
                >
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Owned end-to-end design of the <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Google SecOps Data Export Enhanced Service API</span
                    >, creating LLDs and aligning requirements with Product
                    Managers and senior engineers.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Developed <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >6 APIs across 3 microservices</span
                    > (CRUD + new endpoints) using <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Protocol Buffers</span
                    > and Google's Goa framework; applied feature-flag-based request
                    routing with a <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Spanner-backed</span
                    > data access layer.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Achieved <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >95%+ unit test coverage</span
                    > and performed manual API validation via <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >Google RPC Studio</span
                    >.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .timeline-card {
    transition:
      transform 0.25s ease,
      box-shadow 0.25s ease,
      background-color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .timeline-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }
</style>
